highlights.text: “נשימה” by Chen Aharoni is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 51 spots at #114.
Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “Is It Over Now? (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)” is the highest at #36.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 295 weeks straight.
“תרקוד לנצח” by Omer Adam and Infected Mushroom is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #13.
